Running Code Chunks Click the green “Run” button or use Knit to execute and render the document.

Customizing the Output Echo and Evaluation Options: echo=FALSE: Runs the code but does not show the code. eval=FALSE: Prevents the code from being evaluated. include=FALSE: Runs the code but doesn’t show the code or results.
